### Project Name

Elixpo-Art

### Project Description

This project is an AI-powered art generator that combines a robust backend with a user-friendly frontend. The generator utilizes various machine learning models and algorithms to create unique and captivating artwork based on user input. It allows users to create AI Art, with 10+ themes, 5 unique aspect ratios, 5+ models, and seamlessly generates upto 4 HD pics in under 2 mins (under heavy load).
